title: ELEMENT MAKE IT COUNT - FRANCE 2015
description:
Congrats to DAMIEN PHILIPPE who won the MAKE IT COUNT contest in Paris, France !

Damien won a spot in the European Finals that will take place in Bolzano, Italy, and a chance to win a trip to California to compete for Element sponsorship at Nyjah's park!

Music : El monstrino - Take me to Bahamas or lose me forever
More info : elementmakeitcount.com

OVERALL WINNER : 
Damien Philippe

results : 

UNDER 13 : 
1. Noah Francisco
2. Alexy Moreau
3. Elliot Pressard

14 TO 16 : 
1. Hugo Corbin
2. Lucas Allard
3. Souleyman Diarra

17 & UP : 
1/ Damien Philippe
2/ Damien Ruby
3/ Marc-Alexandre Barbier
